    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-12-01T02:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-12-01T02:00:00-05:00" n="358"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d358">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–150: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Rankin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential   priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Taipei</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-12-01T15:00:00+08:00"
                            >December 1, 1950—3 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>723. Chinese Government hopes that view current developments US can see its way
                    clear to withdraw if possible or at least arrange indefinite <pb facs="0601"
                        n="587" xml:id="pg_587"/> postponement beyond present <gloss target="#t_GA1"
                        >GA</gloss> session of any discussion future of Formosa and on truce action
                    affecting island. Willing continue abide by their undertaking to US in
                    connection President’s neutralization action June 27 but feel that adding <gloss
                        target="#t_UNO1">UNO</gloss> stamp to neutralization and discussing in
                        <gloss target="#t_UNO1">UNO</gloss> whether island should belong to
                    Nationalists or Chinese Communists would place Chinese Government on same
                    footing as Chinese Communists whom US has now officially branded as
                    aggressors.</p>
                <p>Forgoing transmitted on request of Foreign Minister.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rankin</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
